# --- FAQ ---
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "Ko'p so'raladigan savollar"

msgid "Is LingvoCompetence free?"
msgstr "LingvoCompetence bepulmi?"

msgid "Yes! LingvoCompetence is completely free. Register and start learning today."
msgstr "Ha! LingvoCompetence barcha o'quvchilar uchun to'liq bepul. Ro'yxatdan o'ting va bugunoq o'rganishni boshlang."

msgid "How does the gamification system work?"
msgstr "O'yin tizimi qanday ishlaydi?"

msgid "Earn XP by completing lessons, quizzes and vocabulary reviews. Level up, unlock achievements, and compete on the leaderboard!"
msgstr "Darslar, testlar va so'z kartochkalarini bajarib XP ball to'plang. Darajangizni oshiring, yutuqlarni oching va liderlar jadvalida musobaqalashing!"

msgid "Can I get a certificate?"
msgstr "Sertifikat olish mumkinmi?"

msgid "Yes! Complete any course to receive a PDF certificate with QR verification."
msgstr "Ha! Har qanday kursni yakunlaganingizda noyob ID va QR-kod bilan tasdiqlangan rasmiy PDF sertifikat olasiz."

msgid "How long does it take to learn Russian?"
msgstr "Rus tilini qancha vaqtda o'rganib olaman?"

msgid "With 20-30 minutes daily, you can reach A1 in 3 months, A2 in 6 months. Consistency is key!"
msgstr "Har kuni 20-30 daqiqa vaqt ajratsangiz, 3 oyda A1 darajasini, 6 oyda A2 darajasini egallashingiz mumkin. Izchillik — eng muhim omil!"

msgid "What languages is the platform available in?"
msgstr "Platforma qaysi tillarda mavjud?"

msgid "LingvoCompetence supports 3 languages: Uzbek, English and Russian. Switch anytime from the navbar."
msgstr "LingvoCompetence 3 tilda ishlaydi: O'zbek, Rus va Ingliz. Tilni yuqori panel orqali istalgan vaqt o'zgartirishingiz mumkin."

